*. Following five scopes are supported

    1. singleton
    Single instance per Spring IOC container, it's default scope

    2. prototype
    Allows to have any number of object instances

    3. request
    Scopes a bean to an HTTP request only

    4. session
    Scopes a bean to an HTTP session

    5. global-session
    Scopes a bean to a global HTTP session

    3 to 5 are valid only in the context of web aware Spring ApplicationContext container

